h2. Galleries

There are three galleries:
 * a "demo":#demo gallery, that demonstrates some of the most
 interesting features of @ctioga2@ and links to the documentation;
 * a "real life":#real-life gallery that has pictures coming from 
 scientific publications
 * an "index":#index, that links to all @ctioga2@-generated graphs within
 this website, for you to find quickly that specific graph you saw
 ages ago and can't find anymore.

